{"tid":530434,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦freeze 但係滑鼠可以郁 求救","createTime":"2018-01-15T18:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T01:17:10.000Z","uid":123304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85f19f74a9a693bcc4b96933790886567c5ef903","tid":530434,"uid":123304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:06:28.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊Dell inspiron 15 7557 notebook, 大概兩三個月前出現呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n通常出現時間都係打緊機同睇緊youtube, 部機會freeze, 但係滑鼠可以郁。<br />\n<br />\n咁我以為係ram或者hard disk是但一樣有問題, 但係用咗唔同軟件睇過都話無錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n之後懷疑係windows有問題，於是我上個星期正式重裝一次windows。<br />\n<br />\n但係無幾耐就藍屏顯示critical process died。係事件檢視器睇過，顯示 Dump file creation <br />\n<br />\nfailed due to error during dump creation。 完全無頭緒到底係邊度有問題。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打試過有同樣問題可以幫下手，random freeze真係好煩，乜都做唔到。"},{"pid":"a401c62ee35b0a0d40aa064660010a50c4130f35","tid":530434,"uid":123304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"補充 : 每次死機都會有機械聲&quot;綴&quot;一下，唔知關唔關事 求巴打們幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785be255c36be7c5709c814b4e4ec788d9f196ae","tid":530434,"uid":120466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"用dell預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab0aa09b06a70aafca6e0c31f7d48e90144dc5f","tid":530434,"uid":123304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"785be255c36be7c5709c814b4e4ec788d9f196ae","tid":530434,"uid":120466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"用dell預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"我都唔想 有限budget最好係呢部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji